name: 2006 patrons in hic et nunc
description: All patrons with at least one collected OBJKT (before 2021-04-22T19:25:00Z), ordered by the timestamp of their first collect. If you ever collected and object but were too shy to mint one, you should see a blue square on the screen: that's you. Thank you for supporting artists! Click on the squares to see links to patron profiles and their first collected OBJKT. Reported users are in red. This piece complements OBJKT#40252.
